title: Can we get "DAO VOTING" header on website?
body: Since this is a community-run project, I would like to see "DAO VOTING" added to the header tab on the website. This will highlight this unique feature of the project as well as make it easier for newcomers to find and people of the community to vote of proposals.
author: 0x50d6cbcc1Af699255AB3ad2932ef1A23b8f6E64D
